subject: Reasoning
question_en: In a village, some people are poor, some are weak. HAI. Some people are poor and weak. HAI. Some people are weak but not poor. HAI. Some people are poor but not weak. HAI. Select the diagram that captures all these categories.
question_hi: Ek gaon me kuch log garib hai, kuch log kamzuk hai. Kuch log garib aur kamzuk hai. Kuch log kamzuk hai lekin garib nahi. Kuch log garib hai lekin kamzuk nahi. Sab category ko dikane wale diagram chahai. Diagram chahai.
